          "settings": {
            "title": "Our story",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Born in NZ but made in the UK, we’re the purveyor of good times with good people. Our seltzers were created to bring mates together. Get the fun going. At Gerry’s, we’re all about making life feel that little bit… lighter.</p>",
            "page": ""
